window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>An heir without an inheritance. A weak Mage with huge potential and a wealth of experience. A young man living a second life. That's me, Theodore the Babylonian.</p> <p>I am getting to grips with life in Liechtenstein, little by little. But the time has come to get back what is rightfully mine. Most importantly, however, I must show everyone that what's mine is sacred.</p> <p>And anyone who has their eye on it . . . Let's just say, I wouldn't want to be in their shoes.</p>"; 
